title: Tara Palmer-Tomkinson's 14 best quotes on men, money and being an It girl
text:
Previous slide Next slide 1 of 15 View All Skip Ad 
Tara Palmer-Tomkinson , who has died aged 45, found fame as a socialite in the Nineties and was one of the first so-called 'It girls' - famous for being famous. 
Tributes have poured in since the former model's sad death, with friends describing her as witty, generous and bright. Here, we collate some of her best quotes...
